name: More than an END to War, want an END to the beginnings of all WARS.
description:
More than an END to War, want an END to the beginnings of all WARS. This is an original pastel oil physical Art work I created over 10 years ago depicting a soldier at the moment of a blast and the realization of mortality that I have digitally edited and processed through AI Software to come to final image. 
(HQ JPEG 2236x2236 9.20.21) Menace2Metaverse
